xcited to find out we were pregnant with our second child. We thought it would be different since the pregnancy was smoother but our son came early at 23 weeks, weighing 1lb. To look at them now you would never know what a fragile start they had! It's hard to leave your kiddo in the nicu while you go home and It can be especially hard to not be able to hold your child right away. The first time I held my daughter was 14 days after she was born and 27 days after birth for my son. It's not easy waiting for that moment but when it finally comes it is a feeling you can't explain! That is why this Monday's giveaway is for the mama's. 

