#love #pure #pray #doa #miracle #Alloh #aamiin #Gratitude #stayhealthy #staypositive #smile #😊";}i:225;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:0;}i:226;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:3;}i:227;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvD6tuJOCV";}i:228;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:238:"https://scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118696130_617289799160954_1491858581783314766_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=-e4J48loeOsAX_LEelB&oh=d4c80b2636bf699f7b1523af13469236&oe=5F556578";}i:229;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"video";}i:230;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:26941184764;}i:231;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:232;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:233;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:234;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391146835976893620";}i:235;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvD2DkM7S0";}i:236;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599266937;}i:237;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:1412:"My Kingston isn’t having the best day today. That’s the thing about BPD babies. No matter what’s going on, any type of pain or discomfort, it will affect their breathing. My boy still has very weak lungs and his bronchomalacia is acting up today. 

Although Kingston is not in the NICU anymore, he’s never been home. We are up in PICU because we had to finish our vent training to go home. It’s been done but now we are facing other issues that didn’t present themselves until now. As a NICU/PICU mom, I need all the strength and all the patience and all the prayers because like I’ve always said, it doesn’t get easier. I hate seeing retractions or leakage from his g tube. We can be all smiles one minute and super worried the next. Life in the hospital is nothing you can imagine unless you’ve lived it. 

So I’m here to tell you that it’s possible to stay strong. We’ve been doing this since July of last year. You take a crash course in nursing and respiratory therapy. You might even become a doctor ha. Ask all the questions. Learn as much as you can and stay as involved as possible. You are your baby’s voice. 

